snippet.title: The Tribez - Get good vibes - Play The Tribez!
snippet.description:
Play Now! ➡ http://gigam.es/PlayTribez

Visit our website: http://www.game-insight.com
Follow us on Facebook: https://facebook.com/TheTribez
https://www.instagram.com/thetribez/

You are invited to visit a primitive world inhabited by a peace-loving people, who have been hidden beyond a miles-deep portal from time immemorial. Build your own stone-age village, explore territories hidden by mountains and seas, farm fertile lands, and lead your tribe, which considers you sent by the gods, to prosperity. 

The Tribez is a world in which you feel alive!
